    <item>
      <title>加纳总统巴武米亚公布选举宣言，重点关注经济</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/ghana-s-bawumia-unveils-election-manifesto-with-focus-on-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加纳副总统马哈穆杜·巴武米亚 (Mahamudu Bawumia) 是 12 月选举中竞选最高职位的弱势一方，他概述了雄心勃勃的经济增长和预算节约计划，并表示这些计划将有助于维持这个西非国家债务重组后的复苏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/ghana-s-bawumia-unveils-election-manifesto-with-focus-on-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 09:56:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈马斯和伊斯兰圣战组织周日在特拉维夫宣称发动自杀式袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/hamas-islamic-jihad-claim-suicide-operation-in-tel-aviv-sunday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈马斯和伊斯兰圣战组织的军事部门周日晚间声称在特拉维夫进行了一次“自杀式任务”，并警告说，作为对以色列对加沙战争的回应，此类行动将会再次发生。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/hamas-islamic-jihad-claim-suicide-operation-in-tel-aviv-sunday</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 09:50:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>火山烟雾导致菲律宾首都学校停课</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/volcanic-smog-forces-school-suspensions-in-philippine-capital</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾首都南部的一座活火山产生的烟雾导致学校停课，部分地区的空气质量达到“非常不健康”的水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/volcanic-smog-forces-school-suspensions-in-philippine-capital</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 09:32:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>保加利亚总统推迟就临时部长人选进行投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/bulgaria-president-to-delay-snap-vote-over-interim-minister-pick</link>
      <description><![CDATA[保加利亚总统鲁门·拉德夫周一意外拒绝批准新临时内阁，并表示将推迟原定于 10 月举行的提前选举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/bulgaria-president-to-delay-snap-vote-over-interim-minister-pick</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 08:41:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃及延长央行行长任期以显示连续性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/egypt-extends-central-banker-s-rule-in-sign-of-policy-continuity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃及将哈桑·阿卜杜拉的央行行长任期延长一年，此举或将使投资者放心，因为在今年早些时候经历大幅加息和货币贬值之后，这个北非国家将致力于推行正统的货币政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/egypt-extends-central-banker-s-rule-in-sign-of-policy-continuity</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 08:35:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泽连斯基称乌克兰寻求通过入侵为俄罗斯建立缓冲区</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/zelenskiy-says-ukraine-seeks-russia-buffer-zone-with-incursion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽连斯基表示，乌克兰正寻求削弱俄罗斯发动袭击的能力，包括在俄罗斯领土上建立缓冲区，以应对基辅军队继续跨境入侵库尔斯克地区。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/zelenskiy-says-ukraine-seeks-russia-buffer-zone-with-incursion</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 07:37:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平向越南领导人表示，他的目标是建立“友谊”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/xi-tells-vietnam-s-leader-to-lam-he-wants-to-build-friendship</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国家主席习近平向越南总统苏林表示，他愿意同越南领导人发展良好关系。这是苏林就任国家最高领导人以来首次出访。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/xi-tells-vietnam-s-leader-to-lam-he-wants-to-build-friendship</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 04:07:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国法院开始审理他信涉嫌侮辱王室的案件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/thaksin-faces-royal-insult-trial-as-thai-court-begins-hearing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国前领导人他信·西那瓦周一在曼谷一家法庭出庭，法庭开始审查针对他信的侮辱王室案件的证据。几天前，他的女儿刚刚出任这个东南亚国家的新总理。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/thaksin-faces-royal-insult-trial-as-thai-court-begins-hearing</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 03:51:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本领导人候选人及其关键政策立场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/who-could-replace-kishida-candidates-who-could-be-japan-s-new-prime-minister</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本首相岸田文雄上周表示，他不会参加 9 月份执政的自民党总裁选举，此后日本将迎来新领导人。由于自民党在议会中占据主导地位，自民党总裁几乎肯定会成为首相。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/who-could-replace-kishida-candidates-who-could-be-japan-s-new-prime-minister</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 02:41:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
